title: Fredi Evensen Kamtchatka Pirates
description: Fredi ventures into the volcanic peaks of the Kamchatka Peninsula, the land where towering peaks meet the pounding seas. After hitching a ride on some cold war equipment, he finds out why this place has a spot in the heli-boarding hall of fame.
